      <listChange>\n                <change when=\"2016-12-03\" who=\"#JCu\">James Cummings autogenerated EpiDoc output from database</change>\n                <change when=\"2018-03-23\" who=\"#TA\"> Tuuli Ahlholm revised the Epidoc, encoded the text and added an apparatus</change>\n            \t   <change when=\"2020-10-05\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova normalised Unicode</change>\n            \t   <change when=\"2020-10-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages</change>\n            \t<change when=\"2020-11-20\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova added EDCS numbers</change>\n\t\t<change when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography</change>\n\t    <change when=\"2020-12-17\" who=\"#system\">Updated Zenodo DOI</change>\n            \t<change when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references</change>\n                <change when=\"2024-08-01\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag revised from publication and photo</change>\n\t</listChange>\n        </revisionDesc>\n    </teiHeader>\n    <facsimile>\n        <surface type=\"front\">\n            <graphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic000281_tiled.tif\" height=\"2592px\" width=\"1944px\">\n                <desc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo L. Campagna 2004-11-16</desc>\n            </graphic>\n            <graphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic000281.jpg\" height=\"2592px\" width=\"1944px\">\n                <desc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana; photo L. Campagna 2004-11-16</desc>\n            </graphic>\n        </surface>\n    </facsimile>\n    <text>\n        <body>\n            <div type=\"edition\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"la\" resp=\"#TA #JP\">\n            <ab>\n                <lb n=\"1\"/><gap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/> <name><supplied reason=\"lost\" cert=\"low\">Aur</supplied>elio</name>\n                <lb n=\"2\"/><gap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"character\"/><w part=\"F\">rio</w>\n                <lb n=\"3\"/><gap reason=\"lost\" extent=\"unknown\" unit=\"line\"/>\n            </ab>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"apparatus\" resp=\"JP\">\n                <listApp>\n                    <app><note>Text based upon photograph</note></app>\n                    <app loc=\"2\"><note>Manganaro: Pio; Mommsen and Schubring implied R; lapis: R or B</note></app>\n                </listApp>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"translation\">\n                <p><!--translation(s) - add @xml:lang for 'en' or 'it' to div--></p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"commentary\">\n                <p>The text has the form of an honorific with the first line given most prominence. An imperial honorific to an Aurelius is perhaps most likely, as suggested by Manganaro, but line 2 contains a name ending in either -bio (e.g. Fabio) or -rio (e.g. Valerio), and cannot be 'Pio' as proposed by Manganaro.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"bibliography\">\n                <listBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    <bibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"CIL\">\n                        <citedRange>\n                            <ref target=\"http://arachne.uni-koeln.de/item/buchseite/650752\">10.6993</ref>\n                        </citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/GQN8UZSI\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000589</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"AE\">\n                        <citedRange>1989.0339a</citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/R46KDTZX\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001283</ref></bibl>\n                    <bibl>\n                        <author>Manganaro</author>\n                        <date>1989</date>\n                        <citedRange>165 no.23 fig.23</citedRange>\n                        <ptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/EZMBJ6GN\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001831\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001831</ref></bibl>\n                </listBibl>\n\t   <listBibl type=\"discussion\"><bibl/></listBibl>\n            </div>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>\n",
